Jharkhand ke 3 pramukh sthal ek hi raaste par, jo banate hain ek perfect day trip🛕🌴:

1️⃣ Maa Dewri Mandir (Tamar) – Ranchi se 60 km door, yeh 700 saal purana mandir Devi Durga ki 16 bhujaon wali murti ke liye prasiddh hai. Iska anokha architecture bina cement, sirf patharon ko interlock karke banaya gaya hai.

2️⃣ Surya Mandir (Bundu) – Dewri Mandir se 21 km door, rath akar mein bana yeh mandir apni kalatmak rachna aur shanti bhare mahal ke liye mashhoor hai.

3️⃣ Dassam Falls (Taimara) – Surya Mandir se sirf 20 km door, yahaan Kanchi nadi 144 feet ki unchai se girti hai. Yeh prakriti ke premiyon ke liye ek adbhut manzar hai.
Ek din mein dharmik aur prakritik sthal ka anokha anubhav karein!
